Job Description
·       Direct and manage Surge Protection Devices products sales, solution management and growth programs in ASIA Pacific
·       Provide technical presentation and explanation For Surge Protection Devices to the consultants, customer technical team and Distributor to enhance Emerson position so as to facilitate early and decisive closure of business deal opportunities and pursuits.
·       Assist local Sales team, Country Managers and Distributors on pre-sales support through technical consultancy advice to potential customers, and eventually became customers’ preferred choice.
·       Ensure that Company’s quality and professional image in the market are upheld at all times through personal conduct. Good Team work is the essential quality benchmark in all deliverables.
Job Requirements
·        Minimum of Diploma or Bachelor’s Degree preferable in Electrical or Electronic Engineering discipline or equivalent.
·       Possess at least 3 years to 5 years of working experience, doing sales or marketing of electrical component or equipment, with strong background in electrical System design and installation.
·       Able to Communicate in English and Chinese
·        Possess Own Transportation
·        Able to Travel Around Region in Short Notice
·        Excellent interpersonal and organizational skills with a strong commitment to excel
·        Pleasant personality with ability to work with individuals of different levels in the organization
